026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21597,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/12\/good-expected-best-muslims\/","url_meta":{"origin":11644,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Good expected from best Muslims","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 12, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you what distinguishes the best of you from the worst of you? The best of you are those from whom good is expected and people are safe from their evil. The worst\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40743,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/07\/dishonesty-munafiqun\/","url_meta":{"origin":11644,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nifaq: Dishonesty and treachery among hypocrites","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree are in the hypocrite: when he speaks, he lies, when he promises, he breaks it, and when he is trusted, he betrays.\u201d Source: S\u0323ifat al-Muna\u0304fiq li-Abi\u0304 Nu'aym 40 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"http